Day 1. Introducing 100 Days of Generative Patterns.
For the next 100 days I will be creating generative patterns using JavaScript. These patterns are interactive. Each day I will provide a link so you can play with the pattern.  All of these links will work best on a computer, not on a phone. A link to all of the patterns is in the bio above.
